text: Ðis synt ða landgemæra to Bicingtune: ærest of Tornanforda.
Þonne bufan ðam hlince æt ðæs gæredan landes ende.
From Cices wege to ðære bradan æc.
Of Pytleage on Hullingstan, þanon to Dunnes stigele.
Of <þære> stigele to Ecesgeate, ðanon to Brennescumbes geate.
Of ðam geate to Pyrianhammun; <þanon> to Stodfaldun.
Of Wibbanbeorge andlang mearce ðæt eft on Tornanford.
